sentences.sentence: Our Jeanne Moos checked out one innovation1 in New York's Central Park Zoo in the depth of the polar bear pool.

sentences.sentence: Not everyone was entertained though - I definitely heard some low heckling moos and there were even a few walk-outs.
sentences.translation: 当然它们不是都喜欢看“娱乐节目”——我就听到某些家伙会小声地叫着，仿佛在台下起哄，还有几头居然不屑一顾地走开了。”
